Libraries

    streamlit (imported as st): A web framework utilized to instantly turn Python scripts into
                                interactive web applications without requiring front-end development skills.

    plotly.express (imported as px): A high-level data visualization module used to generate interactive,
                                     complex graphs and charts with minimal code.

    pandas (imported as pd): A core data manipulation library used to read, analyze, and structure
                              tabular data (like spreadsheets or SQL tables) into usable objects.

